  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400 degrees Fahrenheit",
    "Season the chicken with salt, black pepper, and paprika",
    "Heat the olive oil in the ceramic tagine over medium heat",
    "Add the garlic and ginger to the tagine and cook for 1 minute",
    "Add the chicken to the tagine and cook until browned on all sides",
    "Add the lime juice, chicken broth, and parsley to the tagine",
    "Cover the tagine and transfer it to the preheated oven",
    "Bake for 30 minutes or until the chicken is cooked through",
    "Remove the tagine from the oven and let it cool for 10 minutes",
    "Serve the chicken and sauce hot over rice or couscous"
